----------------------------------------------------------------
OUT2DISK
Type:  Adverb  (Read)
Use:   Disk number associated with the secondary output file
Null value:  0
       Null value means use any disk having enough space. Usually the
       routines look first on the highest numbered disk and proceed
       downward in disk number if needed.
Tasks:
   SCMAP.......Images, Cleans, self-cals in an iterative loop.
   UTESS.......Deconvolves polarization images by maximizing emptiness.
   VTESS.......Deconvolves sets of images by the Maximum Entropy Method.
